response.overview: Gigi Soto, a twentysomething divorcée and her abuelita Maz are broke, so they need to get creative to get by. Turns out, Maz has tons of protein powder in her garage— a whole inventory she failed to sell for a multilevel marketing scheme. They decide to rebrand the supplements and sell them at a higher price to uppity suburbanites. Things get out of hand when their fraud is figured out by the FBI and they’re recruited to help bring down the CEO of the original protein powder brand.
response.title: ¡WOW!
